name: Hic et Omnes
description:
A celebration marking the successful completion of the Hic et Nunc collab contract project!

It introduces the amazing dev work by @ztepler9000 and @1x1_NFT, supported by the rest of the team – @ktorn, @shamanovitch and @micalnoelson.

This WG3.2 contract presentation from the Hicathon Finale, 26th September 2021 also serves as a guide and work-through for the new contract.
